ucture-templates.1550/)\n* Refer to the Diner prefab in the MasterOfOreon repository for how a saved ST looks like.\n\n# See also\n\n* <Link to StructureTemplate I task>',NULL,0,'MOO - New buildings and upgraded versions',1945600,'https://trello.com/c/KVdgRkF3','5b9b100cca1728134ee88b15','5bb13fe396623c2292321640'),('5bbf59b6e754d06b2fa4b6e8',NULL,1,'2020-09-13 00:02:05.394417','2019-10-16 22:33:40.776000','2020-09-13 00:02:05.394418','{emoji={}}','# Set up a workspace for GooeyJr\n\nGooey is a friendly IRC bot for #terasology on freenode. The bot is written in Coffeescript and is a Hubot. Gooey\'s current abilities include IRC logging, delayed messaging and so on - the list of these can be further extended using Gooey\'s CoffeeScript-based scripting system.\n\nThe goal of this task will be to set up a local workspace containing GooeyJr, successfully launching the bot and connecting it to #terasology on irc.esper.net, then enabling any new script, silly or useful!\n\n# Definition of \'Done\'\n\n* Enter #terasology on irc.esper.net with your GooeyJr with a mentor present and demonstrate the functionality of the script you have enabled.\n\n# Where to start\n\n* Check out the README at https://github.com/MovingBlocks/GooeyJr/ for instructions on setting the bot up. \n* Do comment on the setup instructions so we can improve them.\n\n# Tags\n\n* javascript\n* hubot\n* gooeyjr\n* coffeescript',NULL,0,'Set up a workspace for GooeyJr',1748990,'https://trello.com/c/Ajn4L4pZ','5b9b100cca1728134ee88b15','5da70003a4f3d68a8d822ff2'),('5bbf738ed3824a78cd48d714',NULL,0,'2020-09-13 00:02:05.684320','2018-11-10 02:54:50.346000','2020-09-13 00:02:05.684321',NULL,'# Title (card name)\n\nIntro text - describe the involved stuff (code, component, website, document, etc) briefly, what\'s missing, and what\'s desired\n\n# Definition of \'Done\'\n\n* Put bullet points here for the final state that\'ll satisfy the task\n* Include at least one \"deliverable\" - usually a screenshot for any t