ms could be found record that',NULL,0,'Review of alternative software',131071,'https://trello.com/c/eqw5MnWk','5e844d43482bed3fe97669da','5e844d43482bed3fe97669db'),('5e931d4714732202e62cee0a',NULL,1,'2020-09-12 15:09:09.632729','2020-04-13 00:04:24.842000','2020-09-12 15:09:09.632730','{emoji={}}','See [The safe website](https://scaledagileframework.com/vision/)\n\nRequired Items\n---\n- Details what the software should do\n- How it will differ from competitors\n- A \"Solution Vision\" by SAFE lingo\n\nSuggested points\n---\n- What will this new solution do?\n- What problems will it solve?\n- What features and benefits will it provide?\n- Who will benefit from the system? (I.E: who are _stakeholders_?)\n- What non-functional requirements should the system deliver',NULL,0,'Vision Statement',196607,'https://trello.com/c/9Ycuhms4','5e844d43482bed3fe97669da','5e844d43482bed3fe97669db'),('5e931d67cddfab2a3dbc5fde',NULL,1,'2020-09-12 15:09:09.639556','2020-04-13 00:05:35.793000','2020-09-12 15:09:09.639557','{emoji={}}','Key elements\n---\n- Explaining the understanding of the domain to the release train\n- Done through a video\n- Suggested to use panopto.',NULL,0,'Video Presentation',262143,'https://trello.com/c/d5iD57vY','5e844d43482bed3fe97669da','5e844d43482bed3fe97669db'),('5eabd1dd18524913f14f8f71',NULL,1,'2020-09-12 15:09:16.364341','2020-05-01 17:38:05.774000','2020-09-12 15:09:16.364341',NULL,'',NULL,0,'As a marker, I want to be able to see how many changes a user has made so I tell how much work they did',65535,'https://trello.com/c/L0fKs9x7','5eab97395c130f4aba517da0','5eabd1d35d2a10353e584d07'),('5eabd1e459cea764960ad880',NULL,1,'2020-09-12 15:09:16.374392','2020-05-01 17:38:12.026000','2020-09-12 15:09:16.374393',NULL,'',NULL,0,'As a student, I want to be able to see old versions of the board so that I can see old work',131071,'https://trello.com/c/WbzODCgl','5eab97395c130f4aba517da0','5eabd1d35d2a10353e584d07'),('5eabd1e9547da10de481b0c7',NULL,1,'2020-09-12